     Sniper's terms and conditions

For servers using Sniper,
            in the event that we detect any type of abuse related to a bug in the bot or any other by any means, by the majority of the members of the server or the owner of the server, we hold all rights in order to make leave Sniper from your server and impose an invite ban in it.
For users using Sniper,
            if we find that a user is abusing the bot or abusing its function to intimidate, cause or cause problems for other people, the hosting or the bot, we reserve the right to ban the user from use Sniper for an indefinite period, and contact Discord if necessary.


